event Bid(address indexed token, uint256 id, bytes32 indexed hash, address indexed bidder, uint256 bidPrice)
event CancelOrder(address indexed token, uint256 id, bytes32 indexed hash, address indexed seller)
event Claim(address indexed token, uint256 id, bytes32 indexed hash, address seller, address indexed taker, uint256 price)
event MakeOrder(address indexed token, uint256 id, bytes32 indexed hash, address indexed seller)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
function bulkList(address _token, uint256[] _ids, uint256 _startPrice, uint256 _endBlock, uint256 _type)
function onERC721Received(address, address, uint256, bytes) returns (bytes4)

function orderInfo(bytes32) view returns (uint8 orderType, address seller, address token, uint256 tokenId, uint256 startPrice, uint256 endBlock, uint256 lastBidPrice, address lastBidder, bool isSold, bool isCancelled)
